    public interface Navigatable
    Represents an instance which can be shown in the IDE (e.g. a file, a specific location inside a file, etc).

    Many PsiElements implement this interface (see NavigatablePsiElement). To create an instance which opens a file in editor and put caret to a specific location use OpenFileDescriptor.
